---
// ServicesSnippet.astro
// 「得意分野」と「サービス」を統合するにあたり、まずは現状のセクションを分離して用意します。
---

<section class="relative py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-black">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black font-plus-jakarta mb-16 text-center">
      得意分野<span class="text-red-500">.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">機能追加・開発</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">既存システムの機能追加、API連携、CRUD機能実装など。小規模から中規模開発に対応します。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">3〜30万円</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">1〜10日</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">HP制作・コーディング</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">レスポンシブなHTML/CSS/JS実装。デザインカンプからの完全コーディングに対応。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">2〜20万円</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">1〜10日</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">業務自動化スクリプト</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Python、RPA、業務自動化スクリプト開発。定型業務の効率化を実現します。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">1〜5万円</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">1〜3日</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <a href="#services" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
        詳細を見る
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>